{
  "script_id": "monty-hall",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "舞台上有三扇门，其中一扇后面藏着大奖，另外两扇是山羊。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "你先挑一扇门，比如一号门，但先别打开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "主持人知道奖在哪，他打开一扇有羊的门，再问你：换不换？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "myth",
      "line_id": "myth-1",
      "filename": "myth-myth-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/myth-myth-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "大多数人第一反应是：还剩两扇门，换不换都是一半一半吧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "myth",
      "line_id": "myth-2",
      "filename": "myth-myth-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/myth-myth-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "于是干脆不换，觉得反正机会均等，没必要折腾。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "myth",
      "line_id": "myth-3",
      "filename": "myth-myth-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/myth-myth-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "但这个直觉恰恰错了，答案会让很多人大吃一惊。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "info",
      "line_id": "info-1",
      "filename": "info-info-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/info-info-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "关键在于：主持人不是随便开门，他一定避开奖品，只开有羊的门。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "info",
      "line_id": "info-2",
      "filename": "info-info-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/info-info-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "你最初选中的那扇门，中奖概率始终只有三分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "info",
      "line_id": "info-3",
      "filename": "info-info-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/info-info-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "剩下那两扇门合起来占三分之二，主持人替你排除了其中一扇羊。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "switch",
      "line_id": "switch-1",
      "filename": "switch-switch-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/switch-switch-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "于是那三分之二的概率，全部集中到了没被打开的另一扇门上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "switch",
      "line_id": "switch-2",
      "filename": "switch-switch-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/switch-switch-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "换门，等于押注\"我一开始就选错了\"，而这件事有三分之二会发生。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "switch",
      "line_id": "switch-3",
      "filename": "switch-switch-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/switch-switch-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "所以换门胜率是三分之二，不换只有三分之一，整整差一倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "不信？我们让计算机反复玩这个游戏，画出累计胜率曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "局数越多，换门那条线越贴近三分之二，不换那条贴近三分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "主持人开门泄露了信息，让概率重新分配。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "换门胜率三分之二，不换三分之一，蒙特卡洛模拟一验便知。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "monty-hall",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/monty-hall/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "相信数学，别只信直觉，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 36.08,
  "total_size": 577152,
  "availableVoices": [
